mixin Mission()
    section.mission
        .mission__container.container.reveal-zoom
            div
                +Img({
                        src: 'img/gameplay.jpg',
                        alt: 'Mission'
                    })
            div.colored
                h2 Fast-Paced Fun with Endless Replayability
                p No two climbs in Funtower are the same. Each game offers fresh decisions, new strategies, and unexpected outcomes. It’s the perfect balance of quick rounds and deep strategy—you can play a few short games during a break or spend hours chasing your next high score. 
                p The core mechanics are easy to grasp, but mastering the tower takes practice and smart decision-making. One round you might play cautiously, reaching a modest height; the next, you might take risks and soar past your personal best. This dynamic keeps players coming back, always thinking, "Just one more game."
                +Link({
                    class: 'btn btn-pulse',
                    href: '#game',
                    text: 'Join the Game',
                })